      public Market(int position, int length, int height, Owner owner, Time openTime, Time closeTime) throws InvalidAttributeValueException
      Creates a market object with given values.
      Parameters:
      position - The position of the starting end of this market.
      length - The length between the ends of this market.
      height - The height of this market.
      owner - The owner of this market.
      openTime - The opening time of this market.
      closeTime - The closing time of this market.
      Throws:
      InvalidAttributeValueException - When either of given length and height value is negative.
